Model.Text: It hasn't been long since Diana has stepped up as the Desert Kingdom's new queen.
Merchants have gathered together for a celebration, trying their best to revive a kingdom fallen into despair.
(I just hope this celebration will bring some life back into the sullen hearts of the people...)
Lazer, has everything been secured? These are tense times, I wouldn't want anything to happen during the celebration.
General Lazer? Have you forgotten, your majesty? General Lazer told you he was taking three days off.
(...Oh yeah, he did say something about that. Come to think of it, I don't think I've ever seen my godfather take a day off before...)
